io.simplesource.data

Class FutureResult<E,T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.simplesource.data.FutureResult<E,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - on failure there will be a NonEmptyList of error instances with an error value of this type.
    T - when successful there will be a contained value of this type.

    public final class FutureResult<E,T>
extends Object
    Represents an operation that calculates an Result asynchronously.
